<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 01:18:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>古代DNA在安纳托利亚发现了15,800年前的狗，它们的埋葬方式与人类一样</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ancient-dna-finds-15800-year-old-dogs-in-anatolia-buried-like-humans</link><description>利物浦大学/英国安卡拉研究所在土耳其安纳托利亚中部的两个考古发掘项目中发现了一些最早的狗的证据。研究结果记录在《早期家犬的发展和传播》中&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ancient-dna-finds-15800-year-old-dogs-in-anatolia-buried-like-humans2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 01:18:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ancient-dna-finds-15800-year-old-dogs-in-anatolia-buried-like-humans</guid></item><item><title>《黑客帝国》：谁真正扮演尼奥？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-matrix-who-was-actually-playing-as-neo</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 01:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-matrix-who-was-actually-playing-as-neo</guid></item><item><title>格雷厄姆·奥佩：什么能让我相信上帝？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/graham-oppy-what-would-make-me-believe-in-god</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 00:48:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/graham-oppy-what-would-make-me-believe-in-god</guid></item><item><title>哲学对上帝的最新论证失败了格雷厄姆·奥佩</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/philosophys-newest-argument-for-god-fails-graham-oppy</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 00:33:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/philosophys-newest-argument-for-god-fails-graham-oppy</guid></item><item><title>海狸如何拯救干燥的雨林</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-beavers-save-a-drying-rainforest</link><description>打印/网页复制：&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-beavers-save-a-drying-rainforest.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 00:18:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-beavers-save-a-drying-rainforest</guid></item><item><title>科学家发现蜜蜂缺少的营养物质——蜂群数量激增 15 倍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-uncovered-the-nutrients-bees-were-missing-colonies-surged-15-fold</link><description>科学家们通过改造酵母来生产花粉中常见的必需营养素，为蜜蜂开发了一种突破性的“超级食物”。在对照试验中，喂食这种专门设计的饮食的蜂群的幼仔数量增加了 15 倍，显示出繁殖和整体健康状况的显着提高。随着气候变化和现代农业减少了天然花粉的供应，这项创新可以为支持陷入困境的蜜蜂种群提供一种实用的方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-uncovered-the-nutrients-bees-were-missing-colonies-surged-15-fold.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 00:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-uncovered-the-nutrients-bees-were-missing-colonies-surged-15-fold</guid></item><item><title>宇宙死亡后智慧如何幸存</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-intelligence-survives-the-death-of-the-universe</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 23:48:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-intelligence-survives-the-death-of-the-universe</guid></item><item><title>大脑“清洁”不良会增加患精神病的风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-poorly-cleaned-brain-increases-the-risk-of-psychosis</link><description>日内瓦大学的一项新研究指出，大脑的废物清除系统——类淋巴系统——可能是解决精神病难题的一部分。在患有 22q11.2 缺失综合征（一种高风险遗传病）的人中，研究人员发现 MRI 衍生标记物的发育差异与类淋巴功能有关，以及与海马兴奋/抑制平衡和精神病脆弱性的关联。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-poorly-cleaned-brain-increases-the-risk-of-psychosis2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 23:33:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-poorly-cleaned-brain-increases-the-risk-of-psychosis</guid></item><item><title>研究发现双轨超导量子位产生高保真逻辑纠缠</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/dual-rail-superconducting-qubits-generate-high-fidelity-logical-entanglement-study-finds</link><description>量子计算机是利用量子力学效应处理信息的系统，在某些高级任务上可以超越经典计算机。这些系统依赖于量子位，即量子信息的基本单位，它们通过一种称为量子纠缠的效应相互连接，并共享统一的量子态。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/dual-rail-superconducting-qubits-generate-high-fidelity-logical-entanglement-study-finds2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 23:18:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/dual-rail-superconducting-qubits-generate-high-fidelity-logical-entanglement-study-finds</guid></item><item><title>压电材料为寻找轴子提供了新方法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/piezoelectric-materials-enable-a-new-approach-to-searching-for-axions</link><description>暗物质是一种不发射、反射或吸收光的物质，预计占宇宙中大部分物质。由于它回避了研究普通物质的常见实验技术，因此迄今为止了解暗物质的性质和组成非常具有挑战性。一种假设是它是由称为量子色动力学 (QCD) 轴子的假设粒子组成。这些是理论上的基本粒子，与普通物质的相互作用非常弱，预计它们非常轻、高度稳定且电中性。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/piezoelectric-materials-enable-a-new-approach-to-searching-for-axions2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 23:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/piezoelectric-materials-enable-a-new-approach-to-searching-for-axions</guid></item></channel></rss>